text: A store 8 in Huit in Étretat, France. 8 à Huit is a chain of supermarkets and convenience stores based in France. It is a subsidiary of the French company Carrefour,http://www.franchise-proximite.carrefour.com/nos- enseignes/franchise-8-a-huit/magasin-alimentaire-8-a-huit/ and was founded in 1977. As the name implies, stores are typically open from 8:00 A.M. to 8:00 P.M. local time.http://www.supermarches.org/8-a-huit/ ==See also== * List of convenience stores ==References== ==External links== Category:Carrefour Category:Convenience stores Category:Supermarkets of France Category:Retail companies established in 1977 Category:1977 establishments in France
